# Rename this file to .github/CODEOWNERS after customization.

# Global fallback
* @repo-owner

# Agent governance
AGENTS.md @repo-owner
.ai/** @repo-owner

# CI/CD and GitHub config
.github/** @repo-owner

# Infrastructure
infra/** @infra-owner
infrastructure/** @infra-owner
